N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 96.9 - Handling of crop prior to inspection

State Regulations

Roguing of off-type plants, objectionable crop plants and
weeds is required prior to field inspection. Field boundaries shall be
designated prior to field inspection. Notes
